# 📦 MongoDB Atlas - Social Media Database

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates how to connect to MongoDB Atlas using `mongosh`, create a database, insert data, and perform CRUD & aggregation operations for a simple **Social Media Application**.

---

## ⚙️ Prerequisites

* MongoDB Atlas account
* Database user credentials
* `mongosh` installed on your system

---

## 🔗 Connecting to MongoDB Atlas

```bash
mongosh "mongodb+srv://pradeepg.o022lm4.mongodb.net/" --apiVersion 1 --username pradeepgcs24_db_user
```

> ⚠️ Note: Ensure the correct password is entered. Incorrect credentials will result in:

```
