## 🔍 Query Operations

### Find posts by a user

```javascript
db.posts.find({ userId: 1 })
```

### Find popular posts

```javascript
db.posts.find({ likes: { $gt: 200 } })
```

### Find users with more than 500 followers

```javascript
db.users.find({ followers: { $gt: 500 } })
```

### Projection (specific fields)

```javascript
db.users.find({}, { _id: 0, username: 1, followers: 1 })
```

### Sort & Limit

```javascript
db.users.find().sort({ followers: -1 }).limit(1)
```

---

## ✏️ Update Operations

### Increase followers

```javascript
db.users.updateOne(
  { username: "pradeep_g" },
  { $inc: { followers: 50 } }
)
```

### Update email

```javascript
db.users.updateOne(
  { username: "ravi_kumar" },
  { $set: { email: "ravikumar@social.com" } }
)
```

### Add tag to post

```javascript
db.posts.updateOne(
  { postId: 101 },
  { $push: { tags: "nosql" } }
)
```

---

## ❌ Delete Operations

### Delete a comment

```javascript
db.comments.deleteOne({ commentId: 201 })
```

### Delete low-liked posts

```javascript
db.posts.deleteMany({ likes: { $lt: 100 } })
```

---

## 📊 Aggregation Operations

### Count posts per user

```javascript
db.posts.aggregate([
  { $group: { _id: "$userId", totalPosts: { $sum: 1 } } }
])
```

### Average likes

```javascript
db.posts.aggregate([
  { $group: { _id: null, avgLikes: { $avg: "$likes" } } }
])
```

### Most liked post

```javascript
db.posts.aggregate([
  { $sort: { likes: -1 } },
  { $limit: 1 }
])
```

### Join posts with users

```javascript
db.posts.aggregate([
  {
    $lookup: {
      from: "users",
      localField: "userId",
      foreignField: "userId",
      as: "userDetails"
    }
  }
])
```

