## 📅 Advanced Queries

### Users joined after 2024

```javascript
db.users.find({ joinedOn: { $gt: "2024-01-01" } })
```

### Top active users

```javascript
db.posts.aggregate([
  { $group: { _id: "$userId", postCount: { $sum: 1 } } },
  { $sort: { postCount: -1 } },
  { $limit: 2 }
])
```

